    public class HwMediaImpl
extends CommunicationMediaImpl
implements HwMedia
    An implementation of the model object 'Hw Media'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Description
    • Frequency
    • End Points
    • PHW Services
    • RHW Services
    • Owned HW
    • Band Width
    • Arbiters
